# SAM — Sales Agent Memory

**Persistent, layered memory for AI sales agents.** Stop re-explaining your accounts. Stop re-discovering the same stakeholder relationships. Stop losing context between sessions.

SAM is a structured, file-first memory system shaped specifically for sales workflows — accounts, stakeholders, outreach threads, MEDDPICC qualification states, commercial signals, partner routes. It's inspired by [agentmemory](https://github.com/rohitg00/agentmemory) (which is built for coding agents) and ports the 4-tier consolidation model into a sales-native vocabulary.

> **Status:** v0.1.0 — MVP. Schemas + SQLite storage + 4-tier markdown memory + CLI. See [Roadmap](#roadmap) for what's next.

---

## Why

Sales agents (human or AI) work with state that changes daily:
- New stakeholder identified
- LinkedIn connection accepted / bounced / withdrawn
- Meeting outcome captured
- MEDDPICC element confirmed
- Partner warm-route opened
- Commercial signal published (earnings, leadership move, M&A)

Without persistent memory:
- Every conversation re-explains the territory
- Stakeholder relationships drift
- Outreach cadence collapses
- MEDDPICC gaps stay invisible

SAM keeps that state on disk in a human-readable, AI-loadable shape. Markdown for humans; SQLite for fast indexed retrieval; pydantic for schema validation.

## What you get

- **Sales-native entities** — `Account`, `Stakeholder`, `OutreachThread`, `Touch`, `Meeting`, `Signal`, `Hypothesis`, `Qualification` (MEDDPICC), `WarmRoute`. Vocabulary an AE actually uses.
- **4-tier memory** — L0 raw / L1 atoms / L2 scenes / L3 persona. Same shape as agentmemory's working/episodic/semantic/procedural model, ported to sales.
- **File-first storage** — markdown files are the source of truth; SQLite is an index. Diff in git, edit in your IDE, read on a phone.
- **CLI** — `sam init`, `sam account add`, `sam touch log`, `sam scene <slug>`, `sam search`, `sam persona`.
- **Pydantic schemas** — every entity validates. Easy to plug into MCP servers, FastAPI endpoints, or other agents.
- **MIT licensed** — fork it, ship it, sell it.

## Architecture (one diagram)

```
                  ┌─────────────────────────────────────────┐
                  │  L3 Persona (who is the AE?)            │
                  │  role · pod · methodology · territory   │
                  └─────────────────────────────────────────┘
                                       │
                  ┌─────────────────────────────────────────┐
                  │  L2 Scenes (one per account, narrative) │
                  │  stakeholder · context · motion · entry │
                  │  · last touch · blocker · next action   │
                  └─────────────────────────────────────────┘
                                       │
                  ┌─────────────────────────────────────────┐
                  │  L1 Atoms (dated facts, append-only)    │
                  │  [YYYY-MM-DD] concise fact, max 20 words│
                  └─────────────────────────────────────────┘
                                       │
                  ┌─────────────────────────────────────────┐
                  │  L0 Raw (transcripts, drafts, exports)  │
                  │  unprocessed source material            │
                  └─────────────────────────────────────────┘

  Indexed by SQLite (sam.db) │ Backed by pydantic │ Surfaced via CLI
```

## Quick start

```bash
git clone https://github.com/<you>/sam-memory.git
cd sam-memory
pip install -e .

# Initialise a memory store in the current directory
sam init

# Add an account
sam account add --slug acme-corp --name "Acme Corp" --tier 1 --vertical "Telco"

# Add a stakeholder
sam stakeholder add --account acme-corp --name "Jane Smith" --title "CTO" --meddpicc Champion

# Log an outreach touch
sam touch log --account acme-corp --stakeholder "Jane Smith" \
  --channel linkedin --direction outbound \
  --message "Hi Jane, saw your interview on Q3 platform strategy..."

# Read the scene for an account
sam scene acme-corp

# Search across all accounts
sam search "platform consolidation"

# Show persona
sam persona
```

