## Contributing

This is v0. Issues and PRs welcome — especially around: capture hooks for specific email/calendar providers, MCP server tool definitions, alternative MEDDPICC variants (MEDDIC, BANT), and example data sets for verticals beyond TMT.

Keep proprietary customer / pipeline data out of contributed examples. Use fictional companies (Acme, Globex, Initech) and made-up people.
